%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%B0%E6%94%BF%E7%B8%BD%E5%A4%96%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%88%87%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-david-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%A8%E4%B9%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076556|title=暴雨下堅持獨自和你Lunch   17歲學生：港府回應訴求前會繼續參與  獨媒報導|date=2020-08-18|work=香港獨立媒體網|accessdate=2020-08-22|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208213339/https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076556|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0-lunch-david-%E4%BB%B2%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%95%96%E6%B0%A3%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%9A%9F/|title=連日堅持「和你 Lunch」　 David ：仲有一啖氣都會出嚟|date=2020-06-11|work=立場新聞|accessdate=2020-08-22|archive-date=2020-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923111003/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0-lunch-david-%E4%BB%B2%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%95%96%E6%B0%A3%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%9A%9F/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/483282/%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0lunch-%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E9%8A%B3%E6%B8%9B-17%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3|title=和你lunch｜出席人數銳減　17歲學生不缺席：可透過直播宣傳|date=2020-06-08|work=香港01|accessdate=2020-08-22|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204131135/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/483282/%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0lunch-%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E9%8A%B3%E6%B8%9B-17%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因而被稱為「Lunch哥」{{R|rfa}}。成名後，李國永以「星級抗爭團隊」的名義舉辦示威活動<ref name="oriental">{{Cite news|url=https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20201004/mobile/odn-20201004-1004_00176_034.html|title=「露械照」網上流傳 Lunch哥：你情我願|date=2020-10-04|publisher=東方日報|access-date=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211229130618/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20201004/mobile/odn-20201004-1004_00176_034.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，他在[[周梓樂|周梓樂]]祭壇前與另一名「星級抗爭團隊」的成員玩耍的事件曝光後，該成員不再參與「和你Lunch」活動。

=== 發起「和你睇🍎」行動 ===
